# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Path:         .gitignore
# File:         .gitignore
# Version:      V1.0
# System:       DnD-RSR — D&D 5e Dynamic Reference System
# Module/Role:  Git ignore rules — excludes pipeline intermediates,
#               local backup files, versioned working copies, and OS noise
# Created:      2026-06-13
# Last Updated: 2026-06-13
# ---------------------------------------------------------

# Pipeline intermediate output — generated, never commit
pipeline/data/normalized/
pipeline/data/aggregated/
pipeline/data/verified/

# Pipeline flag
pipeline-needed.flag

# Local backup files
*.bak

# Local versioned working copies (e.g. helpersV12.js, engine-factoryV24.js)
*V[0-9]*.js

# Junk / local output files
results.txt
Pipeline-v3-results.txt
localhost-results.txt
dependency-report.txt
pipeline-dependency-report-dnd-rsr.txt

# Local utility scripts not part of the public project
copy-missing-files.ps1
pipeline-copy-missing-files-dnd-rsr.ps1

# Zip archives
*.zip

# Node
node_modules/

# OS
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store